{"title_page": "List of Mad Men characters", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{in-universe|date=October 2015}}\n{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''Mad Men'' characters}}\nThis is a list of fictional characters in the television series ''[[Mad Men]]'', all of whom have appeared in multiple episodes.\n\n==Overview==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:10%;\" rowspan=\"2\"|Actor\n! style=\"width:10%;\" rowspan=\"2\"|Character\n! colspan=\"8\"|Seasons\n|-\n! style=\"width:10%;\"|[[Mad Men (season 1)|1]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\"|[[Mad Men (season 2)|2]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\"|[[Mad Men (season 3)|3]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\"|[[Mad Men (season 4)|4]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\"|[[Mad Men (season 5)|5]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\"|[[Mad Men (season 6)|6]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\"|[[Mad Men (season 7)|7a]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\"|[[Mad Men (season 7)|7b]]\n|-\n! colspan=\"10\" style=\"background: LightSteelBlue;\" |\n=== Main characters ===\n|-\n|[[Jon Hamm]]\n| [[Don Draper]]\n| colspan=\"8\" {{CMain}}\n|-\n|[[Elisabeth Moss]]\n| [[Peggy Olson]]\n| colspan=\"8\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n|[[Vincent Kartheiser]]\n| [[Pete Campbell]]\n| colspan=\"8\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n|[[January Jones]]\n| [[Betty Draper]]\n| colspan=\"8\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n|[[Christina Hendricks]]\n| [[Joan Holloway]]\n| colspan=\"8\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n|[[Bryan Batt]]\n| [[Salvatore Romano]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background:#ececec; color:gray; vertical-align:middle; text-align:center;\" class=\"table-na\"|\n|-\n|[[Michael Gladis]]\n| [[Paul Kinsey]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CMain|Main}}\n| style=\"background:#ececec; color:gray; vertical-align:middle; text-align:center;\" class=\"table-na\"|\n| {{CGuest}}\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#ececec; color:gray; vertical-align:middle; text-align:center;\" class=\"table-na\"|\n|-\n|[[Aaron Staton]]\n| [[Ken Cosgrove]]\n| colspan=\"8\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n|[[Rich Sommer]]\n| [[List of Mad Men characters#Harry Crane|Harry Crane]]\n| colspan=\"8\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n|[[Maggie Siff]]\n| [[List of Mad Men characters#Rachel Menken|Rachel Menken]]\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CMain|Main}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background:#ececec; color:gray; vertical-align:middle; text-align:center;\" class=\"table-na\"|\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n|[[John Slattery]]\n| [[Roger Sterling]]\n| {{CRecurring}}\n| colspan=\"7\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n|[[Robert Morse]]\n| [[List of Mad Men characters#Bert Cooper|Bert Cooper]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{CMain|Main}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n|[[Jared Harris]]\n| [[Lane Pryce]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#ececec; color:gray; vertical-align:middle; text-align:center;\" class=\"table-na\"|\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#ececec; color:gray; vertical-align:middle; text-align:center;\" class=\"table-na\"|\n|-\n|[[Kiernan Shipka]]\n| [[Sally Draper]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n|[[Jessica Par\u00e9]]\n| [[Megan Draper]]\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#ececec; color:gray; vertical-align:middle; text-align:center;\" class=\"table-na\"|\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n|[[Christopher Stanley]]\n|[[List of Mad Men characters#Henry Francis|Henry Francis]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#ececec; color:gray; vertical-align:middle; text-align:center;\" class=\"table-na\" |\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n|[[Jay R. Ferguson]]\n|[[List of Mad Men characters#Stan Rizzo|Stan Rizzo]]\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#ececec; color:gray; vertical-align:middle; text-align:center;\" class=\"table-na\" |\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n|[[Kevin Rahm]]\n|[[List of Mad Men characters#Ted Chaough|Ted Chaough]]\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#ececec; color:gray; vertical-align:middle; text-align:center;\" class=\"table-na\" |\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n|[[Ben Feldman]]\n| [[List of Mad Men characters#Michael Ginsberg|Michael Ginsberg]]\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#ececec; color:gray; vertical-align:middle; text-align:center;\" class=\"table-na\"|\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CMain|Main}}\n| style=\"background:#ececec; color:gray; vertical-align:middle; text-align:center;\" class=\"table-na\"|\n|-\n|[[Mason Vale Cotton]]\n| [[Bobby Draper]]\n| colspan=\"5\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}{{ref|cast-1|1}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n! colspan=\"10\" style=\"background: LightSteelBlue;\" |\n\n=== Recurring characters ===\n|-\n|[[Mark Moses]]\n| [[List of Mad Men characters#Duck Phillips|Duck Phillips]]\n| colspan=\"4\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n|[[Alison Brie]]\n| [[List of Mad Men characters#Trudy Campbell|Trudy Campbell]]\n| colspan=\"6\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n|-\n|[[Anne Dudek]]\n| [[List of Mad Men characters#Francine Hanson|Francine Hanson]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CNone}}\n|-\n|[[Joel Murray]]\n| [[List of Mad Men characters#Freddy Rumsen|Fred Rumsen]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{CNone}}\n|-\n|[[Crista Flanagan]]\n| [[List of Mad Men characters#Lois Sadler|Lois Sadler]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n|[[Alexa Alemanni]]\n| [[List of Mad Men characters#Allison|Allison]]\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n|[[Talia Balsam]]\n|  [[List of Mad Men characters#Mona Sterling Pike|Mona Sterling]]\n| cols