ata|Zapata]] {{goal|86}}\n|stadium    = [[Itaipava Arena Fonte Nova]]\n|location   = [[Salvador, Bahia|Salvador]], Brazil\n|attendance = 35,572\n|referee    = [[Roberto Tobar]] ([[Football Federation of Chile|Chile]])\n|result     = L\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible|format=1\n|round      = [[2019 Copa Am\u00e9rica Group B#Argentina vs Paraguay|2019 Copa Am\u00e9rica Group B]]\n|date       = 19 June \n|time       = 21:30 [[Brasilia Time|BRT]] ([[UTC-3]])\n|team1      = {{fb-rt|ARG}}\n|score      = 1\u20131\n|report     = http://estadisticas.conmebol.com/html/v3/index.html?channel=deportes.futbol.copaamerica.462520&lang=es_LA\n|team2      = {{fb|PAR}}\n|goals1     = [[Lionel Messi|Messi]] {{goal|57|pen.}}\n|goals2     = [[Richard S\u00e1nchez (Paraguayan footballer)|S\u00e1nchez]] {{goal|36}}\n|stadium    = [[Est\u00e1dio Mineir\u00e3o]]\n|location   = [[Belo Horizonte]], Brazil\n|attendance = 35,265\n|referee    = [[Wilton Sampaio]] ([[Brazilian Football Confederation|Brazil]])\n|result     = D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible|format=1\n|round      = [[2019 Copa Am\u00e9rica Group B#Qatar vs Argentina|2019 Copa Am\u00e9rica Group B]]\n|date       = 23 June \n|time       = 16:00 [[Brasilia Time|BRT]] ([[UTC-3]])\n|team1      = {{fb-rt|QAT}}\n|score      = 0\u20132\n|report     = http://estadisticas.conmebol.com/html/v3/index.html?channel=deportes.futbol.copaamerica.462525&lang=es_LA\n|team2      = {{fb|ARG}}\n|goals1     =\n|goals2     = [[Lautaro Mart\u00ednez|Mart\u00ednez]] {{goal|4}}<br>[[Sergio Ag\u00fcero|Ag\u00fcero]] {{goal|82}}\n|stadium    = [[Arena do Gr\u00eamio]]\n|location   = [[Porto Alegre]], Brazil\n|attendance = 41,390\n|referee    = [[Julio Bascu\u00f1\u00e1n]] ([[Football Federation of Chile|Chile]])\n|result     = W\n}}\n{{Footballbox collapsible|format=1\n|round = [[2019 Copa Am\u00e9rica knockout stage#Venezuela vs Argentina|2019 Copa Am\u00e9rica Quarter-finals]]\n|date = 28 June \n|time = 16:00 [[Brasilia Time|BRT]] ([[UTC-3]])\n|team1 = {{fb-rt|